title: Move the Sticks

description:
Get to know the Move the Sticks podcast with Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks! NFL Network's Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks provide detailed analysis on both the college and pro game from a scout's point of view.
